  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BG Housing Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The most significant expected project-level effect is increased access to housing finance for low and middle income households in Panama, and climate investment in the Panamanian market. Beyond the project-level effect, the proposed project will both promote inclusive home-ownership and financing of climate smart sub-projects in solar power generation, green buildings and energy efficiency.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project consists of a senior loan of up to US$200 million to Banco General, S.A. (the Bank) to be used to finance on-lending activity in Panamas low and middle income mortgage sector and financing of climate smart sub-projects in solar power generation, green buildings and energy efficiency.</narrative>
  </description>
